    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>We compared 23 unvaccinated to 15 vaccinated patients previously infected with SARS-CoV-2 in terms of their aerobic capacity measured by a cardio pulmonary exercise test (CPET). Compared with unvaccinated individuals, those vaccinated had a higher heart rate, higher VO2. Our results suggest objective limitations to exercise capacity in the months following acute COVID19 illness, mitigated by vaccination</jats:p>",
